    "Since 3-paths are chordal graphs, its number of edges is o 3n -6 and they can be drawn in the plane without edge crossing, we can conclude that they are maximal planar graphs, in particular, planar.",
    "Observe that for k ≥ 4, k-paths are non-planar graphs.",
    "Related worksIn this section, we present results from the literature on spectral parameters for k-paths and k-trees.",
